---------------------
--- Copying Files ---
---------------------
Copy [push_deformer.py] to a path defined in MAYA_PLUG_IN_PATH.  For example, the [plug-ins] directory in Maya's preferences.
Copy [apply_push_deformer.py] and [push_deformer.py] to a path defined in PYTHONPATH.  For example, the [scripts] directory in Maya's preferences.

-------------
--- Usage ---
-------------
Simply create an instance of the script, and call the desired function.

	# Create instance of script
	cageedit = CageEdit()

	# Generate cages
	cageedit.generate_cages()

	# Delete cages
	cageedit.delete_cages()

	# Export cages
	cageedit.export_cages()
